data.description: WELCOME HOME! This gorgeous property is located in the highly sought after Woods Addition.  There are lots of updates in this home, including granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and newer roof put on less than 5 years ago! Wood-look ceramic tile throughout the whole home adds warmth and durability! Walking in the front door you are automatically greeted with beautiful tall ceilings and formal dining room. The dining room has a beautiful built-in lighted display cabinet.  There is so much charm and character throughout the entire house with lots of built-ins, storage, and cozy gas log fireplace.  The primary bedroom boasts gorgeous trayed ceilings, TONS of natural light with so many windows. A door from the primary suite to the oversized deck outside, is the perfect place to spend your mornings with a cup of coffee, or evenings watching the sunset behind Cavanal Hill! A large sunroom, off of the dining room is a ideal place for a green room with plants, a reading room, workout space, etc.. the opportunities are endless. The backyard has an idyllic white picket fence. Location is everything with this home, being located so close to Poteau School, shopping, and dining! Buy this house with peace of mind because sellers are providing a one year home warranty on the home!
